<h2 class="wp-block-heading">The Generation AI project addresses three interconnected societal challenges: </h2>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>The weakening of security, control, and sense of agency in a data-driven society</li>



<li>The erosion of trust in authorities, media, science, civil society, and citizens, and </li>



<li>Rapidly growing inequality related to the mastery and agency in constantly evolving information and communication technology.&nbsp;&nbsp; </li>
</ul>


