{% set kadenceInnerHtml %}
<div class="kt-blocks-info-box-media kt-info-media-animate-none"><div class="kadence-info-box-image-inner-intrisic-container"><div class="kadence-info-box-image-intrisic kt-info-animate-none"><div class="kadence-info-box-image-inner-intrisic"><img src="https://www.generation-ai-stn.fi/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Frozen_tired_android_in_blizzard_full_body_slim_s_2ac03fe9-2a0f-4123-91d9-107183b00b46.png" alt="" width="1200" height="1200" class="kt-info-box-image wp-image-97"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="kt-infobox-textcontent"><p class="kt-blocks-info-box-text">The project establishes a foundation upon which technology education for the "AI generation" can be built: technology education that considers the functioning principles of artificial intelligence, the opportunities it offers and its dynamic impacts – without forgetting its shortcomings and risks or how AI systems can increase polarization, discrimination, insecurity, and erode trust.</p>
{% endset %}
{% include "blocks/kadence/infobox.njk" %}

