<div class="kt-blocks-info-box-media kt-info-media-animate-none"><div class="kadence-info-box-image-inner-intrisic-container"><div class="kadence-info-box-image-intrisic kt-info-animate-none"><div class="kadence-info-box-image-inner-intrisic"><img src="https://www.generation-ai-stn.fi/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/ASCII_art_face.png" alt="" width="1024" height="1024" class="kt-info-box-image wp-image-88"/></div></div></div></div></div><div class="kt-infobox-textcontent"><p class="kt-blocks-info-box-text">The project brings together technology developers, schools, authorities, businesses, and civil society organizations. It strengthens children's and young people's ability to face the global societal impacts of technology and produces pedagogical tools for teachers in response to the transformation of learning. </p>
{% endset %}
{% include "blocks/kadence/infobox.njk" %}

