<p><strong>Generation AI</strong>&nbsp;is a project funded by the Strategic Research Council (STN) operating in connection with the Academy of Finland. Generation AI is one of the projects of the&nbsp;<a href="https://www.aka.fi/strateginen-tutkimus/strateginen-tutkimus/strateginen-tutkimus-pahkinankuoressa/ohjelmat-ja-hankkeet/shield" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Security and Trust in the Age of Algorithms (Shield)</a>&nbsp;programme.</p>



<p>The <a href="https://www.aka.fi/strateginen-tutkimus/strateginen-tutkimus/strateginen-tutkimus-pahkinankuoressa/ohjelmat-ja-hankkeet/shield" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Shield programme</a>&nbsp;focuses on security and trust in a world of information technologies and hybrid influence. In addition to more traditional security threats, the threats and opportunities created by digitalization and technological development, as well as various crises from biodiversity loss to climate change, financial crises, and geopolitical conflicts, are reshaping the operational environment in unpredictable ways.&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full is-resized"><img src="https://www.generation-ai-stn.fi/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/72a0207c-4463-469d-803c-10c9a2abb3db-w_960_h_960.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-15" style="width:267px;height:84px"/></figure>


